query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('apache-2.2',
'iphone',
'linux',
'macos',
'networking',
'ubuntu',
'windows')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 10
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Beta',
'Constituent',
'Enthusiast',
'Explainer',
'Fanatic',
'Guru',
'Quorum')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('apple',
'serverfault')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
